            "title": "日股半日跌逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日本股市半日跌逾1%，日經平均指數上午收市報56726點，跌741點，跌幅1.29%。</p>\n</div>",
